Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:11.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:13.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I didn’t see you around, so I decided to go looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:19.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you practice out here every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:21.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Only sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:25.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Being out here, I won’t bother the neighbors if I’m too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:29.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:31.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It’s dangerous for you to\Nbe alone outside this late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It’s all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:37.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It’s right in front of my house,\Nso Dad will come running if I call out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It worries me since you look slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do I look like I’m slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You never thought you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t get down so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I’m just joking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I’m used to you being mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don’t get used to something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:04.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m sorry about having such a dirty mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it’s fine. You wouldn’t be Okazaki-san any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:11.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have you remembered anything about the play you want to perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:23.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I still can’t remember the title,\Nbut it’s a story I was told when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:25.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:34.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It’s a story about a girl left all alone in a world that ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:38.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It’s a very, very sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…story about a winter fantasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.83,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It’s done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.36,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.61,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.99,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A girl in a world that ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:13.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I feel like I’ve seen something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:18.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Though, I don’t know when or where I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I’m sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.32,San,San,0,0,0,,So I’ve been a lead weight on Furukawa Bread?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.33,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.35,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.35,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}Secret Past
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn it, I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What happened this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:39.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I was recommending Sanae’s bread to a customer, but he said it’s so gross that it’s inedible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae overheard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It’s called “rainbow bread”.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.74,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Rainbow to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That made absolutely no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A girl in a world that ended…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:55.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nope, doesn’t ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you think it might be some memory from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have you ever read her a book or told a story like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,No, I don’t recall anything like that. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Ask Sanae about it. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see…{ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right then. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.50,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, brat. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:16.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don’t know what you’re trying to find out. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But, even if you do, don’t tell Nagisa about it. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.32,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Come tell me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why? {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,‘Cause I said so. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:25.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Got it? {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.34,San,San,0,0,0,,No, I don’t remember anything like that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can you give it some thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If it wasn’t a book, could it have been a\Ntelevision show that you watched with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.89,San,San,0,0,0,,Do you know how the story ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:45.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She said it was a sad story,\Nso it probably wasn’t a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.20,San,San,0,0,0,,A sad story…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.12,San,San,0,0,0,,Nothing comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:55.28,San,San,0,0,0,,I’m not very good with sad stories to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:59.52,San,San,0,0,0,,so I don’t think I’ve ever told\Nsomething like that to Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.66,San,San,0,0,0,,Is this something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:13.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I feel like it’s something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:20.02,San,San,0,0,0,,{\fscx108}It’s possible that we might have forgotten about it, and the book you’re talking about is stored somewhere in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.06,San,San,0,0,0,,How about searching for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:25.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. I’ll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.93,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I don’t think you’d find it at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.80,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,We don’t have many picture books or children’s books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess that’s to be expected of a high school library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.68,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,We do have good resources for plays performed at high schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.47,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Would those help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks, but apparently it’s not a theatrical play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.73,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Never mind that, Yukine-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:07:00.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If there are charms that’ll tell me which girls like me, can you teach them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We’re having a serious conversation, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.31,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Yes, I do have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.70,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:11.47,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,First make a heart using your thumbs and index fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:15.62,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Then chant, “To love, to be loved,\Nto dump, to be dumped,” three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:22.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,To love, to be loved, to dump, to be dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.03,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What’s next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:31.24,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Walk around the school once; the first girl who talks to you is the girl who is interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okay! I’m off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.25,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:42.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do girls prefer getting asked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.36,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Furukawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never mentioned her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:52.15,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Of course, hearing “I love you” from\Nthe person they love makes girls happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.76,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,But… the timing is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:08:00.11,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,If you’re too forceful or sudden in\Nyour approach, it may push her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That’s how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.23,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How many laps did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:14.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And no one talked to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.48,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I’ll get a cup of water for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.04,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I think Okazaki-san should try it next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m doing it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.15,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Make the heart with your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m not really interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara, you’re in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:49.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m not sure why, but I feel like I’d have something completely opposite of a romantic relationship with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A hungry bear is roaming around here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you must keep running quietly while playing dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,As if you’re a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:09.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I came looking for you since you’re late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…to dump, to be dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.82,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Out you go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:25.94,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,The first girl who talks to you\Nis the one that cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Everyone’s gathered now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It’s a story I heard long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:41.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don’t remember if I read it in a picture book or if someone told it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The girl was the only person in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It was very sad and very lonely for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:53.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,so she decided to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:58.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It was a doll made by putting together pieces of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:03.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The doll started to move, responding to the girl’s wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:07.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So then, the girl was no longer lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:08.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, I do know this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I found something incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.80,Note,,0,0,0,,Family Welfare
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:24.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I used to go to elementary school with this on my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:30.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dango, dango, dango, dango. Dango—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should have graduated from that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.94,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Who’s the one singing such\Nan embarrassing song inside the shed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:40.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We’re looking for the picture books that\NI read when I was little and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.99,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You won’t find any picture books in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But we might find some if we look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I said that there’s nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:50.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Just go back to your room and flirt with\Neach other like all the other teenagers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:51.04,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What the heck am I encouraging them to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don’t get all excited by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Shut up and just get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:05.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don’t tell Nagisa what I’m about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.44,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don’t tell Sanae that we had\Nthis secret conversation, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don’t want it coming up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:13.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:15.96,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Tea would be nice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanae! Make us some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.54,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, I just said it’s a secret from Sanae, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What kind of brain do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Now we’re fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You see, brat—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.37,San,San,0,0,0,,Here’s your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.72,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:40.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yup. Japanese people have to drink tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:49.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let me remind you again: don’t repeat what I’m about to say to Nagisa or Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Is there something regarding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,‘The hell?! She’s right next to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.25,San,San,0,0,0,,I’ll leave once you’re done drinking, so don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Brat, chug it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You’re not doing this on purpose, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We can finally settle down and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You’re the one making this all complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:17.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I see. Well I don’t care too much about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:22.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don’t care about the potty-chair Nagisa used when she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don’t care about that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You guys were frantically looking for it, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We weren’t looking for a potty-chair! We’re looking for a picture book!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.89,San,San,0,0,0,,Both of you. Night has fallen, so please keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.66,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Whatever. We’ll set the potty-chair aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I said the potty-chair has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then we’ll make this conversation’s codename “potty-chair”.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don’t care about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Let’s continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don’t really care about what you’re looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:51.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But I don’t want you accidently finding a certain other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:52.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A certain other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you don’t want to talk about it,\Nthen I don’t need to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I’ll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don’t want you to get the idea that I have ten thousand hidden porno mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never had that idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:09.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Listen. What’s stored in that shed is my and Sanae’s past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Like old pictures and diaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:16.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What’s in there is the us of the past when we were still chasing our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don’t want that found?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:24.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,When Nagisa was little, something\Nhappened which she almost died from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She had a close brush with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.03,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It was more than ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae was working as a middle school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:40.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Those were busy days, since I was\Nfinally able to pursue what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What was it that you wanted to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.36,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That doesn’t matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:50.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What matters is that we were absorbed within our own worlds, since we had finally been given the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Therefore, we couldn’t make\Nmuch time to be with Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.50,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,One day, Nagisa got a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It was a cold, snowy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The nursery school was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We couldn’t find anyone who could come over to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:14.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But those were busy days for both Sanae and me,\Nso we couldn’t skip a day of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:21.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Her fever was going down, and I could\Ncome home as soon as I finished with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It was only for a span of two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:28.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:35.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa was outside, waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I thought it was a punishment from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:45.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I thought he was taking Nagisa away from us for leaving our daughter alone in order to pursue our careers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:55.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I’m sure there are many people who can handle chasing their dreams and raising their kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.79,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But we couldn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,When Nagisa opened her eyes, we made a vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We swore that we’d always be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.33,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We changed occupations after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:13.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The reason we chose a bakery was because\NSanae said she was confident at baking bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.98,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But you’ve seen the results of when she bakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:19.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So I had to learn everything from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.24,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I had to go into quite a bit of debt, too,\Nso those were rough days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:23.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But it was still kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:27.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And you don’t want Nagisa finding that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Because of what Nagisa would probably think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:34.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That because of her, Sanae and I\Nhad to give up on our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can’t say for sure,{ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:44.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but when I was little, it felt like I did something really bad to Dad and Mom. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa’s starting to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.20,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That’s why we hid all the memories in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:56.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We could have burned them,\Nbut Sanae probably would have cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wouldn’t it be better to tell Nagisa about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:05.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you explain it clearly, I think that\Nshe would have the strength to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:10.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Maybe, but regardless, she’ll probably be shocked if I suddenly slam it in her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.69,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That’s why I’m trying to find the right time to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The truth is always harsh at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Out of the blue, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…here’s a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,There’s something I’ve been planning for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,1: Picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,2: Twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,3: Picric Acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don’t know what the last choice is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.78,San,San,0,0,0,,There is a chemical called picric acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.51,San,San,0,0,0,,It’s an aromatic, nitrous compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:45.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see. I learned something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So, Nagisa, which one’s the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes! 1: Picnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:54.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wrong. The correct answer is 2: Twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.12,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Therefore, tomorrow, we’ll all twitch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:00.88,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa, let’s go on a picnic together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.81,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wait! Don’t leave me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:10.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san. Can I forget about acting tomorrow and enjoy myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sure. You have to take time to recover, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.62,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san, you can enjoy twitching alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.23,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.24,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes, I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.83,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, if you have something you like, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.11,San,San,0,0,0,,I’ll pack it in the bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.37,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I want to eat an apple with rabbit ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dad, you can’t start requesting already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I request hamburger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Then I’ll request shrimp tenpura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:36.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are normal families supposed to be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn’t go. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder what Pop’s doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Someone’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don’t be surprised now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I’m going to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.11,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Picnic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You’re right; it’s not really for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:15.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You think so, too? If I’m there,\NI’ll probably ruin their family trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:19.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But if you do something like this,\Nwouldn’t Nagisa-chan be shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:24.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I did leave a note saying,\N”I have something to do, so please go without me.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Knowing Nagisa-chan, she’ll probably get all worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:33.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Like, “Maybe my home isn’t comfortable for him.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m sure she won’t think that just from me not going on a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:42.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan always lacks confidence in many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Always unsure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That’s how she appears to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She said she was getting confident in herself just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That’s because you’re with her though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:59.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Since you’re there to encourage and yell at her, she can try lots of things and gain confidence, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That’s a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That’s my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She gained confidence because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:13.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But if you turn away from her, what will happen to all the confidence she’s built up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:18.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan doesn’t have a clear\Nunderstanding of how you see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Your indecisive attitude has trapped Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:28.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You ran away from your house,\Nand now you’re running away from hers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:31.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It’s only a bother to me for you to take refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:36.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But, if you resist so strongly,\Nthen I’ll go on the picnic in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:40.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Maybe love will bloom\Nbetween us with this as the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry I bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I’m done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:00.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I’ve been searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Didn’t you read my letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I don’t know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:10.56,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Okazaki-san. We were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Um, didn’t you see my letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I ate it as a side for my breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.48,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Given the time now, we can’t travel someplace anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:23.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I apolo—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:26.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We couldn’t leave because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.24,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So take responsibility and play with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I’m getting some big hits today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.68,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:41.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You’ve fallen in love with me again, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:42.80,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.34,San,San,0,0,0,,You’re wonderful, Akio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Aren’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We didn’t have to go and lay the sheet, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I helped making this bento, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:56.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:02.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:04.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I’m glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:05.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You’re up to bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get in the batter’s box.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:13.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, I’m off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can I swing the bat with my shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:23.99,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All right! Good one, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:26.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Nagisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You fell in love with him again, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn it! So she is in love with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.66,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagisa! You’re up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I’m batting, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.44,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:49.73,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:48.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can do it, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good job, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:58.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Start running, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:01.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
