Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:49.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,This is a world that has ended. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.22,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A world where no one exists aside from myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:04.07,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It’s not about being alone at school or home,\Nbut being alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.54,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It’s a very sad thing, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:09.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s a very sad thing.
